OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fdying out this evening with some late
OL,7,Fsunshine for some. Overnight it will
OL,8,Fcloud over for a time with a few
OL,9,Fshowers before clearing by the morning.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FIt will be a mainly dry day
OL,12,Fwith some good sunny spells, and just
OL,13,Fthe chance of the odd light shower
OL,14,Fover Perthshire. Quite warm.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry on
OL,17,FSunday and Monday with some warm
OL,18,Fspells of sunshine. Becoming cloudier
OL,19,Fon Tuesday with a few showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
